text: Teacher Samantha is great with children and organizes yearly recitals which our family enjoys attending. She regularly updates us on our son's progress, and we feel assured knowing that our son is in good hands.

My nephew performed at the student concert last year at Yong Siew Toh Conservatory of Music. My family was very happy and proud of his performance as we could video it, take photo and keep for memories. It was nice seeing the teacher's other students and their performances too. Overall a very good effort,  the teacher even catered food, I'm impressed as a guest!
The group keyboard class was very engaging. I love that the class only had 2 students, most classes outside have at least 4 or 5 students in a class.
